## Notes

- The prompt → execute → retro session loop documented in CLAUDE.md applies regardless of tool
- Code is the source of truth once written; docs describe intent
- This project is developed across multiple machines and AI tools (Claude Code, GitHub Copilot, Windsurf) — keep all canonical knowledge in `docs/`, not in tool-specific config
